snippet.title: Dance Eden Announcement Trailer | Early Access on Meta Quest (Oct 11, 2024)
snippet.description:
Step into the ultimate XR dance experience with Dance Eden. Show off your moves, join friends, and master original choreographies in a vibrant virtual world!

Enjoy unique, expertly crafted dance routines
Dance with friends in real-time multiplayer sessions
Personalize your avatar and explore visually stunning environments

🎮 Quest Store Link: https://www.meta.com/experiences/dance-eden/8378725502157946/
👾 Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/danceeden

See you on the dance floor! 💃🕺
